#############################

### Test 1: Add Expense
POST http://127.0.0.1:5000/transactions
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "amount": 50,
  "category": "Food",
  "type": "expense"
}

### Test 2: Add Income
POST http://127.0.0.1:5000/transactions
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "amount": 1000,
  "category": "Salary",
  "type": "income"
}

